com.interpss.core.aclf.adj
Interface BranchFlowControl

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
PSXfrPControl, TapControl
All Known Implementing Classes:
BranchFlowControlImpl, PSXfrPControlImpl, TapControlImpl
public interface BranchFlowControl
extends NameTag, IAclfAdjustment

A representation of the model object 'Flow Control'. Aclf branch adjustment/control base class

The following features are supported:

  • Parent Branch
  • Flow Control Type
  • Control Limit
  • Control On From Side
  • Control Spec
  • Control Range
  • Flow From2 To
  • Metered On From Side

See Also:
AclfAdjustPackage.getBranchFlowControl()
